| HistoryText             = The Fast Five were a group of super villains formed by [[Jonathan Swift (Earth-616)|Blue Streak]]. The first time they acted together, they robbed a bank in New York. People soon alerted the [[Mighty Avengers (Cage) (Earth-616)|Mighty Avengers]] of the their activitity. They skated through the city before coming across [[Monica Rambeau (Earth-616)|Spectrum]] and separating to prevent capture. However, the rest of the Mighty Avengers took care of them separately.{{r|Captain America and the Mighty Avengers Vol 1 2}}

The Fast Five appeared as inmates at [[Pleasant Hill]].{{r|Captain America: Sam Wilson Vol 1 8}}
